dct_title_s: Metropolitan Transportation Commission GIS Maps & Data
dct_description_sm: by Bay Area Metropolitan Transportation Commission

These are geospatial data layers acquired from the Bay Area Metropolitan Transportation Commission (MTC) spatial data library. Layers contain feature data related to transportation, administrative boundaries, demographics, environmental factors, census activities, and regional projects. New data layers are added on an ongoing basis.
